\section{Introduction}
\PARstart{T}{his} first chapter introduces all the necessary material to understand the work presented in this thesis. The main technologies and concepts are presented to discover the world of bio-electronic and DNA sequencing.

Section~\ref{sec:DNA_seq} and~\ref{sec:pH_ISFET} explore the chemical bionics and develop the necessary material and concepts. Then, a bio-inspired array and its main characteristic is presented in Section~\ref{sec:Honeycomb}. Finally, the Section~\ref{sec:HEX_app} exposes a particular transistor geometry and its utilization in high speed, small area and good matching applications.

